(1) Replace R104 and R105 with 0R.

(2) Fit R5 as 0R

(3) DNF F5 AND F7

(4) Remove U21 and U22

(5) Remove R148, R149, R150, R151

(6) Fit R147 as 1Mohm

(7) Add R56 and R57 as 82R

(8) Add R41 and R53 as 30R

